{"tid":1971262,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"男子旺角被斬傷昏迷　反黑探員到場調查 (23:47)","createTime":"2020-04-13T18:58:07.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-13T19:05:23.000Z","uid":202340,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"0a0b928619c11e11429d92b6a61ef8ce3283459c","tid":1971262,"uid":202340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-13T18:58:07.000Z","msg":"旺角發生傷人案。今晚（13日）10時許，一對男女途經奶路臣街近通菜街時，約3至4人突然撲出向男子揮刀狂斬，傷者背部及身體多處中刀，昏迷倒卧血泊，行兇者四散逃去，同行女子並無受傷。<br />\n<br />\n傷者友人接獲通知趕至現場了解，救護員到場為傷者作初步包紮，再送院搶救。警方事後臨時封鎖一段奶路臣街，反黑組探員亦奉召到場，暫時沒有人被捕，施襲者犯案動機仍有待調查。<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/article/20200413/s00001/1586792438843/%E7%94%B7%E5%AD%90%E6%97%BA%E8%A7%92%E8%A2%AB%E6%96%AC%E5%82%B7%E6%98%8F%E8%BF%B7-%E5%8F%8D%E9%BB%91%E6%8E%A2%E5%93%A1%E5%88%B0%E5%A0%B4%E8%AA%BF%E6%9F%A5\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20200413%2Fs00001%2F1586792438843%2F%25E7%2594%25B7%25E5%25AD%2590%25E6%2597%25BA%25E8%25A7%2592%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%2596%25AC%25E5%2582%25B7%25E6%2598%258F%25E8%25BF%25B7-%25E5%258F%258D%25E9%25BB%2591%25E6%258E%25A2%25E5%2593%25A1%25E5%2588%25B0%25E5%25A0%25B4%25E8%25AA%25BF%25E6%259F%25A5&d=lExWnqkLii2%2BVYlrfbo%2B8w5Iyec62GFiithg4eFnous%3D&h=782e1037\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20200413%2Fs00001%2F1586792438843%2F%25E7%2594%25B7%25E5%25AD%2590%25E6%2597%25BA%25E8%25A7%2592%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%2596%25AC%25E5%2582%25B7%25E6%2598%258F%25E8%25BF%25B7-%25E5%258F%258D%25E9%25BB%2591%25E6%258E%25A2%25E5%2593%25A1%25E5%2588%25B0%25E5%25A0%25B4%25E8%25AA%25BF%25E6%259F%25A5&h=ae5b2b20\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/article/20200413/s00001/1586792438843/%E7%94%B7%E5%AD%90%E6%97%BA%E8%A7%92%E8%A2%AB%E6%96%AC%E5%82%B7%E6%98%8F%E8%BF%B7-%E5%8F%8D%E9%BB%91%E6%8E%A2%E5%93%A1%E5%88%B0%E5%A0%B4%E8%AA%BF%E6%9F%A5</a>"},{"pid":"1d3e3efedaa042e098df44dbf096a25030fe11a9","tid":1971262,"uid":8014,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-13T19:02:07.000Z","msg":"🖐🏻㊗️<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca9fca435f6603f7a841bd620e93029eb8b2909e","tid":1971262,"uid":36995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-13T19:04:55.000Z","msg":"「同行女子並無受傷」<br />\n<br />\n女權唔衝出黎急取兩性平等？"},{"pid":"454a48303217d16b12479acb60f283e7287d83c7","tid":1971262,"uid":95138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ca9fca435f6603f7a841bd620e93029eb8b2909e","tid":1971262,"uid":36995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-13T19:04:55.000Z","msg":"「同行女子並無受傷」<br />\n<br />\n女權唔衝出黎急取兩性平等？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-13T19:05:23.000Z","msg":"打男人 可恥呀"}]}